data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage block home with charming features and a private oasis in the backyard. This home boasts three spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for family members or guests. The kitchen has been thoughtfully updated with modern soft close Cabinets with pull out drawers and Quartz Counter tops, making meal preparation a joy. The heart of the home is a cozy living room with Cathedral ceilings with a fireplace, perfect for gathering with loved ones on chilly evenings. Step through sliding doors into a screened-in porch, ideal for enjoying the outdoors without the nuisance of insects. This space is versatile and can be used for dining, entertaining, or simply relaxing. This property offers a perfect blend of indoor comfort and outdoor serenity. Whether you're relaxing by the fireplace, enjoying meals on the screened porch, or taking in the tranquility of your private backyard, you'll find this house to be a delightful place to call home.
